sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Button } from 'react-scroll'; import { InfoContainer, InfoWrapper, InfoRow, Column1, TextWrapper, TopLine, Heading, Subtitle, BtnWrap, Column2, ImgWrap, Img, } from './InfoSectionElements'; const InfoSection = () => { return ( {opLine} {headline} {description} ); }; export default InfoSection;
